name: Brass Rectangle Necklace
description:
Dainty little sweetheart of a necklace.

I've hung it from just 24 inches of antiqued bronze chain so it will sit high up on your chest; nestled near your collarbones.

Short enough and lightweight that you can wear it all the time, never take it off, it'll become one of your signature pieces: wear it at work, while you do a downward dog, cook a veggie burger and go for a swim... or just watch Mad Men, whatevs!

name: Bullet Spike Necklace
description:
You are loving this bullet trend we are seeing everywhere in the jewelry world, but alas you are not so keen on wearing a bullet around your neck... well lookey here: a solution in the form of a spike that is bullet'ish! 

She is just under an inch and a half in length and solid brass. Looks amazing layered with all you other Sweet Harriet necklaces!

You can order it on a short ot long chain so it with either sit on your chest (V-neck zone) or long and lovely (just under your bra line). Choose your own adventure!

name: Mini Spike Necklace
description:
You love to layer, you love spikes, you love this necklace!
How sweet it is to be loved by you!

Half an inch in size this little sweetheart of a spike will quickly become your new most favorite wear with everything necklace.

I've hung it from 12 inches of chain so it sits nice and high and shows off your clavicles ... oh my what beautiful clavicles you have!

name: Brass Spike Necklace
description:
Badass Chic.

One and a half inches of solid brass hung from 18 inches of antiqued bronze chain. 

Sits like a arrow pointing at your cleavage... if you should be so lucky as to have any cleavage ;)

name: Brass Column Pendant
description:
Solid brass & strikingly simple.

Two inches long & less than a quarter of an inch wide; Hung from 30 inches of  antiques bronze chain. Total length of the pendant is 17 inches.

Great for layering.

name: Vintage Painted Pattern Diamond Lockets
description:
Diamonds are a girls best friend... 

1.5 inches long by 1.5 inches wide hung from 32 inches of assorted chain

Necklace is a total length of 16.5 inches. The lockets are a quarter of an inch thick. Double sided, patterned on both sides.

Available in pink, teal, baby blue, black, red, orange and white.

Feel free to let me know your color preference or stock your shop with the whole lot!

name: Glass Bubble Drops
description:
So delicately beautiful... like bubbles.... its very difficult to be in a bad mood and say bubbles.

I've designed all three option to sit showcased on your upper chest. (from approximately 10 inches of dainty chain)

The largest glass bead (the teardrop shape) is hung from a Y-styled chain; the bead is approximately an inch long.

The second largest bead (the flat pressed oval) is half an inch wide and a quarter of an inch thick.

The tiny little sphere (aka the orb)  is just over a quarter of an inch in size. Like a sweet pea....actually perhaps I'll start calling them sweet peas instead of orbs..

name: Glass Orb Pendants
description:
Itty bitty round handblown glass bead necklace filled with natural goodness.

They are under half an inch in size... dainty, delicate and pretty....they remind me of you. (Yes, I am flirting with you...call me ;) 

I'll send you a surprise filled orb unless you let me know you preference.

Your orbs may be filled with dandelion seeds, sand, antler dust, dried flowers, lavender, cranberry seeds, feathers, or some other random natural tiny object.

name: Glass Oval Pendants
description:
So sweet, these flattened little orbs are just over half and inch wide and long and 1/4 of and inch thick.

I fill these beauts with a bunch of delicious fillings:
*sand *lavender *flowers *antler dust *kisses (jk! But if I could I would)

Feel free to message me with your requests or I will surprise you; boo!

Hung from 32 inch chain; long and lovely pendants.

name: Glass Teardrop Pendants
description:
Oooh! 

Dainty glass teardrops, inch long and just over 3/4 inch at it's widest point. 

I fill these tear drops with a variety of goodies: sand, flowers, lavender, sawdust, dandelion seeds, itty bitty feathers...

Feel free to make requests otherwise I will surprise you with the fillings.... 
Oh my goodness isnt this fun!

name: Shabby Chic Teeny Weeny Locket
description:
Cutest lil' lockets ever made!

Only half an inch wide and three quarters an inch long. 

Hung from long 32 inch chain, they are the ultimate layering locket.

I make these little beauties in a variety of patterns, feel free to let me know if you have a preference otherwise I will keep you on your toes and surprise you!

name: White Shabby Chic Medium Sized Lockets
description:
I may have an addiction to distressed paint... I may need a shabby chic intervention...

Sweet Harriet fans are loving this variation of locket. Not too big,not too small it's just right at 1.25 inches. 

Hung long chains (32 inches) so they hang just below your bra line. 

If you have a preference of images let me know otherwise I will surprise you...welcome to living life on the edge.

name: Quadruple Fold Out Lockets
description:
These are so cool. They fold out accordion style so that you can fit not one, two or three pictures of your favorite children, but you can fit a fourth picture in there of...Brad Pitt. Mmmm. Brad Pitt.

They are 1.25 inches long, 0.75 inches across and 0,25 inches thick. Hung long on 32 inches of chain.

name: Geometric Earrings (pack of 4 pairs)
description:
It's hip to be square...and triangle ...and circle... and lets be honest, it's hippest to be hexagon.

Four pack of all four designs. They are dainty danglies all hanging approximately and inch long. All are hung from lead free, nickel free (therefore irritation free) ear hooks.

Suggested retail of $22.00.

If you are interested in single pairs contact me or visit my etsy shop:
www.etsy.com/shop/SweetHarrietCo

name: Geometric Necklaces (pack of 4)
description:
Geometric Jewelry is in like flynn.

Stock your shop with all four designs. Tiny brass shapes; all are around half and inch in size and I've hung them from 18 inch long chains so they sit high up on your chest; perfect for layering.

Suggested retail at $22.00 each.

If you are interested in purchasing just one of these beauties contact me or visit my etsy shop:
www.etsy.com/shop/SweetHarrietCo

name: Glass Lockets
description:
Coming in a variety of square, diamond, oval, large round, medium round. 
Variety of goodies pressed inside from feathers, leaves, flowers and lace.

All lockets are easily opened and closed so your customers can put inside their own little keepsakes

All hung on long (32") chain.

I suggest stocking your store initially with at least four of them so you can see the different styles and see which ones your customers respond to.

Let me know if you have any requests :)

name: Copper WInking Owl
description:
This little Owl is a total Hoot!

He plays in a band with his fish friends called : Hootie and the Blowfish

Seriously. Seriously though... 

Your new winking winged copper friend is 1.5 inches long and 0.5 inches wide.

I've hung him from antiqued copper chain and you can choose if you'd like to wear him long (32 inches) or up on your chest bone (24inches)

Hoot. Hoot.

name: Brass Snake Pendant
description:
I may or may not have a fear of snakes. I dont want to talk about it...

However, I LOVE this little guy. He's quite sweet and is only 2.5 inches and therefore not very scary at all.

He comes in bronze, black and white. Feel free to specify if you have a preference. If not specified when you order one you will get bronze, two you'll receive white and bronze and three orders you will get all three colors for your boutique.

I've dangled him from a deliciously long (32 inch) antiqued brass chain.

name: Mini Heart Lockets Variety Pack
description:
BIG LOVE for Miniature Heart Lockets

Stock your shop with these sweethearts! Order multiple mini lockets... as many as you'd like!! Just increase the quantity when you checkout. (click on the shopping cart on the top right)

I'll send you a variety of min heart lockets (0.75 inch across, 1 inch long) all on 12 inch antiqued brass chains.

*Make sure to have your wholesale discount code handy for checkout*

name: Turquoise Shiva Peace Pendant
description:
Mini Silver Shiva paired up with a tear drop turquoise bead dangling off a brass peace symbol.

The peace symbol is 1.5 inches hung from a long 32 inch antiqued copper chain so the total length of the necklace 17.5 inches long.

Peace yo.

name: Four Square Wrought Iron Pendant
description:
Wrought Iron Pendant is just under two inches long and an inch wide.

Hung from 31 inches of antiqued bronze chain

name: Iron Heart Pendant
description:
The only hearts that cannot break are made of love...and wrought iron!

The heart is an inch and a half long and almost an inch wide. 

The unbreakable heart is hung is from a 31 inch long antiqued bronze chain

name: Patina Blue Wrought Iron Pendant
description:
Curly Cue Wrought Iron Pendant bathed in a blue patina.

The pendant is 1.75 inches long and an inch wide.

I've hung it from a 31 inch long chain so it will hang just over 17 inches long.

name: Mehndi Wrought Iron Pendant
description:
Found objects make the best necklaces. It's a fact.

This wrought iron trunk latch design reminds me of Mehndi henna art... hung from a deliciously long chain antiqued brass chain. 

The pendant piece is two inches long and just over an inch and half wide, hung from a 31 inch long chain; so the necklaces will hang just over 17 inches down.

name: Mini Telescope Pendant
description:
Fully functioning mini telescope, to indulge your inner peeping tom. Dont worry I wont tell anyone... Sure, sure it's to look at the stars...wink wink.

It's an inch and a half closed and three inches fully extended. Hung from a 16 inch long antiqued brass chain.

You are going to love your new point of view;)

name: Miniature Harmonica Pendants
description:
How quirky are theses little babies?! And big BONUS they actually work!

Your co-workers are gonna LOVE it when you play them their favorite songs all day at work on your mini harmonica necklace!

Available in gold, silver, red, black & blue. All hung on long 30 inch chains.  The harmonica itself is an inch and half long so the necklace will hang a total of 16.5 inches long.

$28 for one harmonica pendant

name: Dream Catcher Earrings
description:
Carry Sweet Harriet's original design hand beaded Dream Catcher earrings in your sweet boutique. 

Feel free to specify which color palate you or your customers would prefer. If you order more than one set of earrings I'll send you a variety of colors. (Increase your quantity in the shopping cart checkout page)

Five inches long, hung on 14k gold plated earring hooks. So cool.

name: Long Dangly Gypsy Bead Earrings
description:
Hand pressed clay and filigree beads hung from oblong hoops.

Just over 3 inches long.

So pretty.

description:
Silver, gold, black or white filigrees filled with:
Baby blue, light pink, olive green, turquoise blue, hot pink, black or white clay  
Oh me oh my the options are endless!

Hung from sterling silver or 14 carat gold plated hooks = irritation free:)

Feel free to request custom color combos... or try your luck and I'll send you a bevy of exotic looking beauties to stock your shop.

$26.00 each

name: Tubular Antler Necklaces
description:
Cowabunga!  Tubular dude!  

These tube necklaces range from 0.5-2 inches long.  I hang them from a variety of chain; black, silver, bronze...all cut to sit higher up on your chest bone. 

Increase your quantity in the checkout page; If you only purchase one tubular necklace you will be receiving a mini tube slice on a 7 inch long antiqued bronze chain. Beyond that I will send you a delicious variety of necklaces to stock your sweet shop.

name: Wholesale Medium Sized Locket Variety Pack
description:

ie: graphic patterns, feathers, Native American theme etc.

name: Brass Magnifier Pendant
description:
Perchance you were one of those kids that fried bugs on the sidewalk with the power of sunlight and a magnifying glass? Well then this necklace is for you.  Fry bugs to your hearts content with this hand dandy magnifier around your neck at all times!

The magnifier itself is 2.5 inches long. The actual glass area is an inch across and it's hung from 15 inches of antiques brass chain so the total length of your new necklace is almost 18 inches long.

name: Lil' Gold Compass
description:
I love this little one.

Gold Compass itself is just over an inch in size and it packs a powerful punch. Black face, silver type on the face and BONUS: it totally works!! 
I've hung it from a long antiqued bronze chain; the total length of the necklace is almost 19 inches.

You'll never be lost again.

name: Flock in Flight
description:
Make me a bird, so I can fly far far away...

Brass locket is 2 inches by an inch and a half wide.
Space for two of your favorite pics inside.

Hung from 15 inches of brass chain. Long and lovely.

name: Nautical Calender Pendant
description:
Soooo you forget what day it is and your iphone battery is dead...or you are in the middle of the sea and have no cell service?! What does one do??? Well fret no more little sailor, your solution has arrived...wear a calender around your neck!

It is a fully functioning solid brass nautical calender, and it goes all the way up to the year 2054. Amazing grace.

The pendant itself is an inch and a half hung 16 inches down on antiques brass chain.

name: Vintage Painted Pattern Lockets
description:
Vintage meets shabby chic. These sweet little betties are a real hit with ladies of all ages.

They are 1 inch in length and I've hung them from a variety of 13 inch long chain, so it hangs longer but not too long. 

Room for two wee photos inside.
Available in green, blue, pink, orange, red, black, white and silver accents.
Feel free to specify which colors you want in your notes when you check out. This listing is for one locket; if you do not specify what color you'd like I will be sending you the white locket. Load up on more variety by increasing your quantity upon check out.

Merci Beaucoup!

name: Knotty Necklaces (Black, Copper & Bronze)
description:
The most versatile necklace you will find!

Clean and simple, two stands of sturdy chain tied in a knot; it's not rocket science but it sure looks good!

I've secured the knot in place so no worries about it coming undone. And I've put a clasp on the back of the necklace so there will be no reason to mess your perfect 'do!

This listing is for one black, one bronze and one copper knotty necklace, all priced at $28.00.  

If you would like to order just one or the other, send me a quick email and I'll make it happen for you!

name: Knotty Necklaces (Gold & Silver)
description:
The most versatile necklace you will find!

Clean and simple, two stands of sturdy chain tied in a knot; it's not rocket science but it sure looks good!

name: Trio set of Three Prong Antler Necklaces

Hung from 7 inches of chain these sweet little babies sit higher up on your chest bone.  At $22/ necklace, with this purchase you will get one of each metal to stock you store with...

if you would only like only one antler necklace, please refer to my etsy website for solo purchases. www.etsy.com/shop/SweetHarrietCo

Thank you:)

name: Antler Slice Earrings
description:
No two pairs are alike! All sliced on my Dad's farm on the prairies from Antler sheds; no animals were hunted or shot to produce these pretty little pairs of earrings.

This listing is for one pair of earrings. Please feel free to order multiples by increasing your quantities in the check out page.

Depending on the size of the antler shed these earrings range from 1-2 inches long. I hang them from a mix of findings. All my hooks are lead free and nickel free, therefore they should be irritation free!

name: London Anchor Swivel Magnifying Glass Pendant
description:
What do you get when you combine London with an anchor and a magnifying glass???
A MagniLondanchor . Obviously!

And this amazing MagniLondanchor really works!
It swivels either way so it is left handed friendly! 

Its an inch and half long and half an inch wide. When swiveled fully open it's 2.25 inches long.
I've hung it from a 16 inch long antiqued brass chain so its a total 17.5 inches long.

name: Dragonfly
description:
Symbolically rich and (I think) quite beautiful; Two dragonflies are better than one.

Brass locket is two inches by an inch, opens up to two spots for your favorite photos; hung on 15 inches of antiqued brass chain.

name: Howdy Sailor!
description:
Double sided locket: ship at sea on one side, pretty lil' lady on the other side = win win.
Winning!

Locket is an inch and a half long by an inch wide, hung from 15 inches of antiqued brass chain.

name: Feather Weight
description:
Delicately detailed locket with a wee lil' feather in the center. 

An inch long by .75 inch wide; hung from 15 inches of antiqued brass chain.

Pretty.

name: Black and White Delicate Design
description:
Ooooh how pretty! 
This lil' locket will go with everything you ever wear... EVER. Ever? Yep! Ever.  

Mini locket (under an inch) hung from 15 inches of antiqued brass chain.

name: Mini Seahorse
description:
Itty bitty lil' seahorse and a mini starfish dangling side by side. Best friends for life.

The little locket measures in under an inch all around. 
Opens up to keep two of your mini photos of your miniature lovers & friends.

Hung from 15 inches of antiqued brass chain.

name: Red Oak Locket
description:
Oh Oak trees how I love thee...

Brass locket is two inches by an inch and a half.

Hung from 15 inches of intricate antiqued brass chain.

name: Stag Locket
description:
Just a couple of handsome Stag's hanging out on the horizon, no big deal.

A big ol' brass locket that measures in at 2inches by an inch and a half hung from 15 inches of brass chain.

name: Distressed Black Flower Filigree
description:
Large matte back flower-like filigrees that are lightweight and so versatile. 

I've hand distressed them so bits of dark bronze peak through showing off all the delicate detailing.

The filigree is two inches wide by two inches tall. The total length of these earrings after they have been hung from the fish hooks is just under 3 inches.

name: Black Gypsy Discs
description:
Matte black filigree discs dangling from shiny black chain, hung from black hooks. Three inches long and two inches across.

I get compliments on these black beauties every time I wear them:-)

Wander with wonder little gypsy, for you are free.

name: Spanish Dancer Black and Turquoise Earrings
description:
Delicately distressed black filigrees dangle from shiny black chain on bronze fish hooks; finished off with a little round turquoise beads. 

The are long and lovely at 4 inches but worry not they are quite lightweight and will not stress your pretty ear lobes.

Pretty. Exotic. Pretty exotic!

name: Patina Green Hinge Earrings
description:
Perhaps I went deep sea diving and retrieved a couple of hinges from a sunken ship and then I went straight home and made you some beautiful earrings with them, you're welcome!!!

They are a total of 3.25 inches long, linked together with antiqued bronze findings; the round stone dangling at the bottom is a piece of hematite that's been dyed to look like light turquoise.

name: Antler Tips From my Pa's Farm
description:
...So my Dad finds these antler sheds on his farm in southern Saskatchewan. He slices them, drills, polishes and varnished them creating one of a kind, rustic, super cool necklaces... and then I quite simply thread a chain through the center and take all the credit!!! Thanks Dad:-)

Hung from 26" of a variety of chain. (feel free to let me know if you have any preferences) The total length of the necklace is 15 inches.

Please keep in mind these little beauties are random acts of nature and each one will vary in size and color... which I think is a great thing because each one is as unique as you are!

name: Large White Flower Filigree
description:
Soooo pretty! 

Large flower-like filigrees that are lightweight and so versatile. 

They are a fresh white and I've hand distressed them so bits of dark bronze peak through showing off all the delicate detailing.

The filigree is two inches wide by two inches tall. The total length of these earrings after they have been hung from the fish hooks is just under 3 inches

name: Antiqued Airplane Necklace
description:
How cool is this necklace?!!! I LOVE it!!! And bonus: the propellers actually spin!!!

It made of brass'; it's vintage; and it's definitely unique!

The plane is just under four inches across and just over and inch at it's widest point. I've hung it from 9 inches of thick antiqued bronze chain. Let me know if you'd prefer it on longer or shorter chain. Right now it should hang midway up on your upper chest.

name: Medieval Sword Bracelet
description:
The sword itself is just under 3 inches long. 
The total length of the bracelet is 7 inches. You can clasp it anywhere along the chain. Convo me if you'd like a larger bracelet. I created it so that it would sit close to your wrist to prevent the sword from flipping around; but if you are into flipping just let me know...

name: Under the Sea Sword Bracelet
description:
This sword was probably found in a treasure chest that had been buried for centuries under the sand out at sea. It probably belonged to a powerful but miniature Ruler of an ancient island that sunk and it can probably grant you three wishes... and cook you dinner.

This small but mighty sword is just under three inches long. Total length of the bracelet is seven inches. Feel free to let me know if you'd prefer if longer or shorter.

name: Poseidon's Sword Earrings
description:
If Poseidon carried a sword instead of a trident spear, he would definitely have carried one of these... take my word on this; I know stuff.

A total of three inches in length including the antiqued bronze earring hooks. I've wire wrapped them and them used a resin glue to secure the wire in place so these little puppies are sure to stay together, forever.

name: Medieval Sword Earrings
description:
I have a feeling these are magical swords. I dont know for sure. But I have a feeling...

They are just over three inches long hung on antiqued brass hooks. Wire wrapped in gold and securely appoxied.... My heart would break if you were to buy these and one were to fall off somewhere in the world. My heart would break into so many pieces that even a magical sword couldn't repair it.

name: The Original Alley Cat Pendant
description:
From my "Alley Cat" series; Inspired by a dresser I found in a back alley that had beautiful drawer pulls on it. I deconstructed them and made this pendant and have since been searching out other interesting and industrial handles to take apart.

It's cast iron (I assume) and has a beautiful natural aged patina; accented by copper findings and hung from a fantastically long antiqued bronze chain (15 inches). The iron piece itself is an inch by two inches long; the total length of the necklace is almost 17 inches.

Careful what you throw out in your back alley, I just might make jewelry out of it:-)

description:
Powerful, strong and free, hear her roar! Rrrrrooooaaaarrrr!

(I know this pendant has a big manly main on it, but lets pretend in the world of jewelry that females have manes, ok? ok.)

This awesome little beauty is only about an inch in size but she packs a powerful punch! She's been 'antiqued" and hung from 11 inches of sturdy bronze chain.

Rise up and roar kitten roar!

name: Rosie's Ring
description:
From my "Alley Cat" series; Inspired by a dresser I found in a back alley that had beautiful drawer pulls on it. I deconstructed them and made jewelry (of course) and have since been searching out other interesting and industrial handles to take apart.

name: Little Blue Mermaid
description:
Next life I want to come back as a mermaid. And I want my best friend to be a dolphin. 

These little bathing beauty is four and a half inches long and a half inch wide. I've patina all my mermaids myself so there may be slight variation from the photo. I've hung her from 7.5 inches of antiqued bronze on either end of her, but she likes to hang at a slight tilt upward as shown in the photo. 

She's so lovely.

name: Brass Bow Tie
description:
Coolest necklace EVER. End of discussion.

The brass "bow tie" is a vintage filigree that measures three inches across and and inch and a half wide. I've strategically hung it from new "antiqued" bronze chain so it sits high on your chest like a bow tie! The total length of the necklace/ choker is seven inches long.

name: Vintage Silver and Brass Oblong Locket
description:
This pretty little vintage locket has a flower sunburst wreath highlighted in silver. 
It's an inch and a half long and just over an inch across. It opens from the right and has room for two of your favorite pics inside and has a simple cross hatched pattern on the back.

I've hung it form a shiny 12 inch long snake chain; The total length of the necklae is 13.5 inches.

name: Gold Chief Sitting Bull Locket
description:
A transparent image of Chief Sitting Bull on 1.5 inch round gold locket. It opens from the right, there's room for two of your favorite photos on the inside; the back is shiny gold.
I've hung it from a nice long 16inch antiqued bronze chain.

Chief Sitting Bull was a Lakota Chief.He is notable in American and Native American history for his role in the major victory at the Battle of the Little Bighorn against Lt. Col. George Armstrong Custer. Seven months after the battle, Sitting Bull and his group left the U.S. to Wood Mountain, Saskatchewan, where he remained until 1881, at which time he surrendered to US forces. After his return to the United States, he briefly toured as a performer in Buffalo Bill's Wild West show.

My Grandma was born in Wood Mountain, and my family still resides on a farm not far from Wood Mountain. Hence my appreciate for Chief Sitting Bull:-)

name: Parakeet Pin
description:
Polly want a cracker? Nope! Polly wants this pretty little pin!

This quirky little gold brooch is only an inch and a half but paired with the beautiful red and yellow feathers it reaches almost three inches in size. 

You can wear it as a brooch, slide it onto a bobby pin and wear it in your hair or on a chain as a necklace. If you'd prefer to put it on a chain, I can put a jump ring on it, free of charge:-) I can also sell you a gorgeous gold chain if you need one, just let me know.

name: Lil' Squirrel Pin
description:
This is the cutest brooch EVER! 
The little gold squirrel filigree is about an inch in size; with the red and black feathers it's a total of two and a half inches tall.

I can attach a jump ring free of charge if you want to have the option of wearing it as a necklace.
A gorgeous redhead purchased one of my pins at a music festival and slid it on a bobby pin and transformed it into a cute little barrette! (see last photo)

The options are endless and you are in charge!

name: Flower Power
description:
These beautiful vintage copper flowers are two and half inches long/wide.  
I put a small accent amber colored multi-facet bead in the center of the earring and hand painted the patina on them. 
They are hung from antiqued bronzed rings and earring hooks. (rubber backings included) Total length: 3 inches  

Please note this is a real patina on them so please take care of your new most favorite earrings by not bathing, swimming or hot tubbing while wearing them.

name: Glam Rock (Large)
description:
A total of four inches top to bottom these black beauties are large and in charge!

Lightweight, delicate and intricate these bold beauties have been delicately distressed by hand; the highlights of gold peaking though the matte black create an eye-catching combo.

Each filigree is an inch and three quarters in diameter and hung from shiny lead and nickel free gold plated fish hooks.

name: Shabby Chic (Large)
description:
Deliciously long and delicately distressed.

Two large white filigrees each measuring 1.75 inches across, hung from gold fish hooks, hanging a total of four inches long.

Matte white highlighted with shiny gold.

name: Classy Dame (mini's)
description:
These little beauties are Versatile with a capitol V! They will soon become your favorite pair of go-to earrings.

Three intricate filigrees each an inch in diameter; with the gold fish hooks they measure three and a half inches long. 

Lightweight but sturdy; intricate and delicate; fancy, but not too fancy; holy moly me oh my, I LOVE these earrings!

name: Glam Rock (mini's)
description:
Three and a half inches of black and gold equals three and a half inches of pure rock n' roll!

I've distressed the three inch round gold filigrees with matte black, delicately joined them and hung them from shiny gold ear wires.

Get down with your bad self.

name: Shabby Chic (mini's)
description:
Pretty and delicate just like you:-)

Three distressed white filigrees hanging delicately from gold ear wires. Each pretty little flower is one inch in diameter; the total earring length including the fish hooks is 3.5 inches long.

name: Verdigris Diamonds
description:
Intricate filigrees hand coated in verdigris patina and hung from pewter colored fish hooks.

These earrings look amazing on redheads, pop against black hair and glow on blonds, making them the ultimate gift!

Filigree measures: 1.75" x 1.75"
Total earring length: 2.25"

name: Sneaky Snake
description:
A sexy slithering bad ass addition to your collection of cool jewels.

The snake itself is 2.5 inches long by 2 inches tall; it's been hand painted to accentuate the details and rock 'n roll style. It's hung from 8 inches of antiqued large loop chain. The beauty of this chain is that you can clasp it anywhere you'd like depending on your neckline.

Sssssssasssy!

name: Big Bold Bat
description:
Holy cool necklace, Batman!!

Check out that wing span! This lil' brass bat is four and a half inches across and only a half inch wide. I've hand painted this handsome lil' devil to enhance the details. It's hung from nine inches of gold chain on either side and then I've dangled more gold chain that hangs two inches below the bat. It hangs a total of 10.5 inches long.

name: Big Bad Bull
description:
Cowgirls are hot.

Two and a half inches across, one and a quarter inch long this brass bull packs a powerful punch. I've hung this little dude from 9 inches of dainty twisted loop, gold chain and I hand painted the brass pressing with cream paint to pick up on all the little details.

Giddy-up!
